      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Nathan Sturtevant</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:107px;\"><a href=\"https://www.movingai.com/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/91/Nathansturtevant.jpg\" width=\"105\" height=\"125\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Nathansturtevant.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Nathan Sturtevant <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Nathan R. Sturtevant</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist, games- and AI-researcher and programmer, and professor at  Department of Computing Science, <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a>. \nHe received his Ph.D. on <a href=\"/Games\" title=\"Games\">Multi-Player Games</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_California,_Los_Angeles\">University of California, Los Angeles</a> in 2003 under advisor <a href=\"/Richard_Korf\" title=\"Richard Korf\">Richard Korf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nBeside Multi-Player Games, his research interests include <a href=\"/General_Game_Playing\" title=\"General Game Playing\">General Game Playing</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pathfinding\">Pathfinding</a>. \nIn 2006 and 2007 he worked with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BioWare\">BioWare</a> to implement a pathfinding engine for the game <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dragon_Age:_Origins\">Dragon Age</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Sturtevant&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Sturtevant&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Richard_Korf\" title=\"Richard Korf\">Richard Korf</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>On Pruning Techniques for Multi-Player Games.</i> <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2000\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI-2000</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/papers/multi_prune.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>  (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-40031-8_8\">A Comparison of Algorithms for Multi-player Games</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2002\" title=\"CG 2002\">CG 2002</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/papers/comparison_algorithms.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Multi-Player Games: Algorithms and Approaches</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_California,_Los_Angeles\">UCLA</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_20\">Current Challenges in Multi-player Game Search</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2004\" title=\"CG 2004\">CG 2004</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Sturtevant&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11922155_2\">Partial Information Endgame Databases</a></i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_11\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 11\">Advances in Computer Games 11</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/papers/partialEndgameDatabases.pdf\">pdf</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ru.is/faculty/yngvi/pdf/BjornssonSS06.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Adam_White&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Adam White (page does not exist)\">Adam White</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-75538-8_11\">Feature Construction for Reinforcement Learning in Hearts</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2006\" title=\"CG 2006\">CG 2006</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.cs.du.edu/~sturtevant/papers/heartsfeatures.pdf\">pdf</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/talks/CG2006Talk.pdf\">slides as pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>An Analysis of UCT in Multi-Player Games</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#31_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 31, No. 1</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_4\">An Analysis of UCT in Multi-player Games</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2008\" title=\"CG 2008\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Max_Barrer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Max Barrer (page does not exist)\">Max Barrer</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Neil_Burch&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Neil Burch (page does not exist)\">Neil Burch</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Memory-Based Heuristics for Explicit State Spaces</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2009\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 2009</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/papers/TDH.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vadim_Bulitko&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vadim Bulitko (page does not exist)\">Vadim Bulitko</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>TBA*: Time-Bounded A*</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2009\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 2009</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mesut_Kirci&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mesut Kirci (page does not exist)\">Mesut Kirci</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Feature Learning Using State Differences</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~jonathan/publications/ai_publications/GGPfeatures.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Sturtevant&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeffrey_Long&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeffrey Long (page does not exist)\">Jeffrey Long</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Buro\" title=\"Michael Buro\">Michael Buro</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Timothy_Furtak&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Timothy Furtak (page does not exist)\">Timothy Furtak</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.5555/2898607.2898629\">Understanding the Success of Perfect Information Monte Carlo Sampling in Game Tree Search</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2010\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2010</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/papers/pimc.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Carsten_Moldenhauer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Carsten Moldenhauer (page does not exist)\">Carsten Moldenhauer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Single-Frontier Bidirectional Search</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2010\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2010</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~jonathan/publications/ai_publications/sfbds.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Anthony_Valenzano&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Richard Anthony Valenzano (page does not exist)\">Richard Anthony Valenzano</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#KBuro\" title=\"Mathematician\">Karen Buro</a>, <a href=\"/Akihiro_Kishimoto\" title=\"Akihiro Kishimoto\">Akihiro Kishimoto</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Simultaneously Searching with Multiple Settings: An Alternative to Parameter Tuning for Suboptimal Single-Agent Search Algorithms</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/aips/icaps2010.html#ValenzanoSSBK10\">ICAPS 2010</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~jonathan/publications/ai_publications/dovetailing.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vadim_Bulitko&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vadim Bulitko (page does not exist)\">Vadim Bulitko</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a> (<b>2010</b>). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/On-learning-in-agent-centered-search-Sturtevant-Bulitko/db9ebcd72ffd7008bafb91ce9d9110c5682fa0a5\"><i>On learning in agent-centered search</i>. [https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/atal/aamas2010.html#SturtevantBB10 AAMAS 2010</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#MGoldenberg\" title=\"Mathematician\">Meir Goldenberg</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>,  <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>  (<b>2010</b>). <i>Portal-Based True-Distance Heuristics for Path Finding</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/socs/socs2010.html#GoldenbergFSS10\">SOCS-10</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~jonathan/publications/ai_publications/portals.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mesut_Kirci&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mesut Kirci (page does not exist)\">Mesut Kirci</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s13218-010-0081-8\">A GGP Feature Learning Algorithm</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/journals/ki/ki25.html#KirciSS11\">KI Vol. 25</a>, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/Uzi_Zahavi\" title=\"Uzi Zahavi\">Uzi Zahavi</a>, <a href=\"/Robert_Holte\" title=\"Robert Holte\">Robert Holte</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Zhifu_Zhang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Zhifu Zhang (page does not exist)\">Zhifu Zhang</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Inconsistent Heuristics in Theory and Practice</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_%28journal%29\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 175, Nos. 9-10, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~jonathan/publications/ai_publications/inconsistent_heuristics_draft.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Maxim_Likhachev&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Maxim Likhachev (page does not exist)\">Maxim Likhachev</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Wheeler_Rum&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Wheeler Rum (page does not exist)\">Wheeler Rum</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Heuristic-Search-Comes-of-Age-Sturtevant-Felner/18e0bf9e6f28e151c0cf60ba1e962f0c1fb6ed23\">Heuristic Search Comes of Age</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2012\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2012</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Max_Roschke&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Max Roschke (page does not exist)\">Max Roschke</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>UCT Enhancements in Chinese Checkers Using an Endgame Database</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2013\" title=\"Conferences\">CGW@IJCAI 2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~nathanst/papers/UCT-endgame.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Marc_Lanctot\" title=\"Marc Lanctot\">Marc Lanctot</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Pepels&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tom Pepels (page does not exist)\">Tom Pepels</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Monte Carlo Tree Search with Heuristic Evaluations using Implicit Minimax Backups</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/cig/cig2014.html#LanctotWPS14\">CIG 2014</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1406.0486\">arXiv:1406.0486</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Guni_Sharon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Guni Sharon (page does not exist)\">Guni Sharon</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Exponential Deepening A* for Real-Time Agent-Centered Search</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2014\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2014</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#MGoldenberg\" title=\"Mathematician\">Meir Goldenberg</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#RoniStern\" title=\"Mathematician\">Roni Stern</a>,  <a href=\"/index.php?title=Guni_Sharon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Guni Sharon (page does not exist)\">Guni Sharon</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Robert_Holte\" title=\"Robert Holte\">Robert C. Holte</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.jair.org/index.php/jair/article/view/10882\">Enhanced Partial Expansion A*</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Artificial_Intelligence_Research\">Journal of Artificial Intelligence Research</a>, Vol. 50</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Sturtevant&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>  (<b>2015</b>). <i>Challenges and Progress on Using Large Lossy Endgame Databases in Chinese Checkers</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2015\" title=\"Conferences\">CGW@IJCAI 2015</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#MGoldenberg\" title=\"Mathematician\">Meir Goldenberg</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alon_Palombo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alon Palombo (page does not exist)\">Alon Palombo</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://content.iospress.com/articles/ai-communications/aic743\">The compressed differential heuristic</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.iospress.nl/journal/ai-communications/\">AI Communications</a>, Vol. 30, No. 6</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>A Brief History and Recent Achievements in Bidirectional Search</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2018\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2018</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Shuli_Hu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Shuli Hu (page does not exist)\">Shuli Hu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ijcai.org/Proceedings/2019/175\">Direction-Optimizing Breadth-First Search with External Memory Storage</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2019\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 2019</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-65883-0_13\">On Strongly Solving Chinese Checkers</a></i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_16\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 16\">Advances in Computer Games 16</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a>, <a href=\"/Abdallah_Saffidine\" title=\"Abdallah Saffidine\">Abdallah Saffidine</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>Computer Games Workshop at IJCAI 2018</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#41_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 41, No. 2</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Sturtevant&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dor_Atzmon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dor Atzmon (page does not exist)\">Dor Atzmon</a>, <a href=